{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"011d821beb","title":"关于同意中、苏、蒙对修中蒙铁路的意见的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ebc6bddfaa","index":0,"year":1952,"month":9,"day":6,"articleId":"011d821beb"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"270144b00c","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"011d821beb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指周思来1952年9月4日关于同意苏蒙两国提出的中苏蒙三国对修中蒙间铁路协定的报告。报告说，协定草案的中心问题有四：（一）双方（中国为一方，苏、蒙为一方）对修铁路至中蒙边境；（二）双方均按一五二四公厘宽轨修筑；（三）今年开始勘察设计，1953年动工，1955年内完成；（四）该路由内燃机车牵引，具备每尽夜对开十二次列车的能力，将来经协议提高到每尽夜对开二十四次列车。关于协定公布时间，我们表示同意斯大林的意见，待铁路修成后再行公布。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a070f70e92","type":"title","text":"关于同意中、苏、蒙对修中蒙铁路的意见的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"011d821beb"},{"id":"270144b00c","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"011d821beb"},{"id":"ef7c9342c3","type":"paragraph","text":"九月四日电收到。同意你们关于中苏蒙铁路的意见，并同意待铁路修成后再行公布协定","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"011d821beb"},{"id":"e76f829259","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"011d821beb"},{"id":"2d6737732c","type":"paragraph","text":"九月六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"011d821beb"}],"page":{"id":"f0709841fe","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"011d821beb","start":232,"end":232}}}},"__N_SSG":true}